    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is pristine, still retaining that new-car scent with no signs of wear on the upholstery or trim. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and zero issues. Buyers can expect a top-tier driving experience in a vehicle that has been cared for with the highest standards.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
